        <item>
          <title>Amazon Workers Strike Over Labor Agreement</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Thousands of Amazon workers at seven facilities went on strike Thursday, demanding a labor agreement with the e-commerce company. The Teamsters union called it the largest strike yet against Amazon in the US.]]></description>
